@1175 = ~Plate Armor~
@1176 = ~Duskwood Plate~
@1177 = ~This finely crafted suit of armor is fashioned from layered duskwood. While it offers the solid defense of conventional plate, it remains lighter and more attuned to natural energy. 
Its organic structure allows even single-class druids to don it without breaking their sacred oaths.

